==English==

===Noun===
'''pardon'''  (''plural:'' [[pardons]])
# A specific act of pardoning; as an official pardon, freeing a prisoner from jail.

====Translations====
*Spanish: [[indulto]] {{m}}

===Verb===
'''to pardon'''  ([[pardons]], [[pardoned]], [[pardoning]])
# [[Relieve]] of [[guilt]]

====Translations====

* French : [[grâce]]
* [[w:Ido|Ido]] : [[indulgo]]
* [[w:Swedish language|Swedish]] : [[förlåta]], [[ursäkta]]

===Interjection===
'''pardon'''?
# Used when not [[understand]]ing the [[meaning]].

====Translations====
*[[w:Swedish language|Swedish]] : [[ursäkta]]?, [[förlåt]]?, [[va]]? (''highly colloquial'')


